                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13091252" author="rickhall" created="Thu, 25 Aug 2011 19:40:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Modified framework to allow bundles to add listeners/services while in the STOPPING state. The only non-obvious issue was that we had to invalidate the bundle context early to avoid race conditions where runaway threads in bundles could still do stuff after their activator stop() method had returned.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
